# ─── For Vercel ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Frontend is a single-page app. Vercel handles routing.
# API calls go to your VPS backend — set the URL below.

# Set this in Vercel Environment Variables:
# VITE_API_BASE=https://your-vps-ip:8080

# The frontend reads this at runtime to know where the API lives.